{
  "stem": "304.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was the first time I saw him, but not the last time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then later, we found out that he made experiments on human beings and on twins, and we were very lucky we didn't step out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Another thing that I remember from this situation when we were walking-- one of my aunts with her teenage daughters was in front of us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she was-- I always knew she's 10 years older than my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So if my mother was 43, she had to be in her early 50s.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And somehow, when she-- Mengele didn't talk too often, but once in a while, he talked, and this was one of those rare occasions.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, I always say, he even touched me once.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Later when we're at other selections, once he touched me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he looked at my aunt, and he said, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she looked back at him, and she snapped back, 35.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he let her go with her daughters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of her daughters just visited me a few weeks ago, and I told her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She didn't-- doesn't remember it, and I know why.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember because she said 35, and I knew she was older.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is why I remember this incident.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what I'm trying to say here-- her mind worked so fast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was a very bright woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She died already in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That she knew that 35, for whatever reason, sounds so much better than to say 50.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And another aunt who was with her five younger kids from eight-- she didn't give up her kids to the grandmother, and she was sent to the left.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
